  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.6.8">
<l>kaḻimiṉṟoṇ ṭīrkaḷ kaḻittut</l>
<l>toḻumi ṉavaṉait toḻutāl</l>
<l>vaḻiniṉṟa valviṉai māḷvit</l>
<l>taḻiviṉṟi yākkan tarumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let them pass, slaves. Making [them] pass</l>
<l>worship. If you worship him,</l>
<l>making die [your] harsh karma that stands in the way</l>
<l>he will give [you] bodies free from decay.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
